	(text_box "This is the output from the battery pack. The colors described is for the 4 core battery cable.\n\n1) V_{BAT}: Cable to supply power to camera. Wire Color: \n2) V_{SENSE}: Just used to sense the voltage of the cells. Color: \n3) GND: Power and Sense Ground. Color: \n\nFor the 4th wire in the cable. Color: . Cut it short and do not attach to PCB. This was used for charging the lime 42V battery packs so not usable here.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
